{% comment %}
  Recharge Affinity Customer Portal — Order Summary Card
  =======================================================
  Renders an order summary card on the Affinity portal overview page
  matching the Figma design (order-summary desktop 740x505 / mobile 354x454).

  Strategy:
  - JS IIFE (NOT a web component) that:
    1. Waits for Recharge SDK readiness with a retry loop.
    2. Authenticates via recharge.auth.loginCustomerPortal().
    3. Fetches active subscriptions, upcoming charges, addresses, payment methods.
    4. Fetches product images via Shopify AJAX API (/products/{handle}.js).
    5. Builds and injects the order summary card DOM into the portal.
  - CSS uses BEM naming with cf-order-summary block prefix and !important
    overrides matching the existing reskin pattern.
  - If JS fails, the portal still renders natively (graceful degradation).
{% endcomment %}

{%- capture svg_info_circle -%}<svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="6.5" cy="6.5" r="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/><text x="6.5" y="10" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.4" font-family="FT System, sans-serif" font-weight="400" fill="currentColor">i</text></svg>{%- endcapture -%}

<style>
  /* ===================================================
     Order Summary Card — cf-order-summary BEM block
     =================================================== */
  .cf-order-summary {
    border: 1px solid #D9E8F4 !important;
    background: #FFFFFF !important;
    border-radius: 4px !important;
    padding: 0 18px 20px 18px !important;
    display: flex !important;
    flex-direction: column !important;
    gap: 20px !important;
    box-sizing: border-box !important;
    font-family: 'FT System', var(--font-body--family), sans-serif !important;
    margin-top: 16px !important;
  }

  /* --- Section headings --- */
  .cf-order-summary__heading {
    font-size: 20px !important;
    line-height: 26px !important;
    letter-spacing: -0.2px !important;
    color: #202635 !important;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    font-family: 'FT System', var(--font-heading--family), sans-serif !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
  }
  .cf-order-summary__heading:first-child {
    padding-top: 20px !important;
  }

  /* ===================================================
     Product card — "In your order" section
     =================================================== */
  .cf-order-summary__products {
    display: flex !important;
    flex-direction: column !important;
    gap: 8px !important;
  }

  .cf-order-summary__product-card {
    display: flex !important;
    flex-direction: row !important;
    gap: 20px !important;
    align-items: center !important;
  }

  /* Image container with rotated background rects */
  .cf-order-summary__product-image-wrap {
    position: relative !important;
    width: 92px !important;
    height: 92px !important;
    flex-shrink: 0 !important;
  }
  .cf-order-summary__product-image-bg {
    position: absolute !important;
    top: 0 !important;
    left: 0 !important;
    width: 92px !important;
    height: 92px !important;
    background: #F2F7FB !important;
    border-radius: 4px !important;
    transform: rotate(3.1deg) !important;
  }
  .cf-order-summary__product-image-bg--secondary {
    position: absolute !important;
    top: 0 !important;
    left: 5px !important;
    width: 82px !important;
    height: 92px !important;
    background: #ECF7FF !important;
    opacity: 0.15 !important;
    border-radius: 4px !important;
    transform: rotate(3.1deg) !important;
  }
  .cf-order-summary__product-image {
    position: relative !important;
    z-index: 1 !important;
    width: 100% !important;
    height: 100% !important;
    object-fit: contain !important;
    display: block !important;
  }

  /* Quantity badge */
  .cf-order-summary__quantity-badge {
    position: absolute !important;
    bottom: 0 !important;
    left: 0 !important;
    z-index: 2 !important;
    width: 23px !important;
    height: 23px !important;
    border-radius: 63px !important;
    background: #202635 !important;
    display: flex !important;
    align-items: center !important;
    justify-content: center !important;
